snippet.title: Best VGM 1383 - Mario Paint - Creative Exercise
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Mario Paint (1992)
Creative Exercise
Hirokazu Tanaka, Ryoji Yoshitomi & Kazumi Totaka
